<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <section class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Our Services</h1>
            <p>Comprehensive solutions for your engineering needs</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services-details-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="service-detail">
                <div class="service-image">
                    <img src="/images/service1.jpg" alt="Fabrication & Erection">
                </div>
                <div class="service-text">
                    <h2>Fabrication & Erection</h2>
                    <p>We specialize in the fabrication and erection of various steel structures, piping systems, and storage tanks. With over 30 years of experience, we have successfully executed numerous projects across different industries including power plants, refineries, and chemical plants.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Steel Structure Fabrication & Erection</li>
                        <li>Piping Systems</li>
                        <li>Tank Fabrication</li>
                        <li>Various Engineering Construction Works</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-detail reverse">
                <div class="service-image">
                    <img src="/images/service2.jpg" alt="Industrial Coating">
                </div>
                <div class="service-text">
                    <h2>Industrial Coating</h2>
                    <p>Through our group company Romecca HP Coats, we provide high performing protective coating solutions for various industrial applications. Our expertise includes specialized industrial coatings for leading Indian and multinational organizations.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Protective Coatings</li>
                        <li>Epoxy Painting</li>
                        <li>Sandblasting</li>
                        <li>Decorative Painting</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-detail">
                <div class="service-image">
                    <img src="/images/service3.jpg" alt="Project Management">
                </div>
                <div class="service-text">
                    <h2>Project Management</h2>
                    <p>Our project management team works on time schedules, procurement schedules and manpower needs to ensure smooth execution of projects. We conduct regular quality checks and safety inspections throughout the project lifecycle.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Project Planning</li>
                        <li>Quality Control</li>
                        <li>Safety Management</li>
                        <li>Execution & Handover</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="machinery-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Machineries and Tools</h2>
            <div class="machinery-grid">
                <div class="machinery-category">
                    <h3>Machineries</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Welding Rectifire (memco) - 30 EA</li>
                        <li>Grinding Machine AG-7 - 15 EA</li>
                        <li>Grinding Machine AG-5 - 8 EA</li>
                        <li>Buffing Machine GQ-4 - 8 EA</li>
                        <li>Magnetic Drill Machine - 3 EA</li>
                        <li>Hand Drill Machine - 3 EA</li>
                        <li>Compressor - 10 M/s</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="machinery-category">
                    <h3>Tools</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Fitter Tools - 30 SET</li>
                        <li>Welder Tools - 30 SET</li>
                        <li>Spanner Set 6 TO 32 DE - 40 SET</li>
                        <li>Spanner Set 6 TO 32 Ring - 40 SET</li>
                        <li>Torque Spanner - 4 SET</li>
                        <li>Box Spanner 8mm to 32mm - 4 SET</li>
                        <li>Dp Kits (Developer, Penetrant& Cleaner) - 20 SET</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="machinery-category">
                    <h3>Measuring Instruments</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Vermeer Caliper - 50 UOM</li>
                        <li>Master Lavel 4"6 - 40 EA</li>
                        <li>Master Lavel 12' - 20 EA</li>
                        <li>Micrometer Outsides - 20 EA</li>
                        <li>Micrometer Insides - 20 EA</li>
                        <li>Measuring Tape 3mtr/5mtr - 100 EA</li>
                        <li>Measuring Tape 30 mtr - 40 EA</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>